Package org.kuali.kfs.gl.service

Interface Summary
AccountBalanceService This interface delcares methods useful for dealing with AccountBalance objects.
BalanceService An interface which declares methods needed for using Balance
CollectorDetailService Services that deal with Collector Details
EncumbranceService An interface declaring services dealing with encumbrances
EntryService An interface declaring methods to deal with Entry
ExpenditureTransactionService This service provides basic functionality to manipulate Expenditure Transactions
GlCorrectionProcessOriginEntryService Implementations of this interface are used to store a list of origin entries to be used by the GLCP.
NightlyOutService This interface defines the batch jobs that would be run nightly against the pending general ledger entries.
OriginEntryGroupService An interface of methods to interact with Origin Entry Groups
OriginEntryService An interface of methods to interact with Origin Entries
PosterOutputSummaryService Interface for service methods which support the poster output summary report
PreScrubberService  
ReversalService An interface with methods to interact with reversals
ScrubberService An interface declaring methods needed to run the scrubber
ScrubberValidator An interface that declares methods that would be needed to validate origin entries and transactions run through the scrubber
SufficientFundsService Service used for manipulating disbursement voucher cover sheets.
SufficientFundsServiceConstants Holds constants for transfer of funds document.
 

Class Summary
ScrubberReportData A class which encapsulates statistics about a scrubber run
